@startuml NezhaCyberMCP_时序图
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "WenQuanYi Micro Hei"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
    BorderColor #2980B9
    FontColor #1A252F
}

skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
    BorderColor #F39C12
}

skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor #EAF7EA
    BorderColor #27AE60
}

title 哪吒网络安全 MCP - 请求与数据同步时序图

' ============================================================
' 参与者
' ============================================================
actor "AI 客户端\n(Claude / Cursor)" as Client
participant "MCPServer\n(mcp.go)" as MCP
participant "Actions\n(actions.go)" as Actions
database "数据库\n(PostgreSQL / DSQL)" as DB
participant "AdvisoryJob\n(advisory_job.go)" as Job
participant "CirclService\n(circl.go)" as Circl
participant "MycertService\n(mycert.go)" as Mycert
participant "CIRCL API\n(外部)" as CirclAPI
participant "MyCERT 门户\n(外部)" as MycertPortal

' ============================================================
' 阶段一：服务器启动（本地模式）
' ============================================================
== 阶段一：服务器启动（本地模式） ==

[-> MCP : main() IS_LOCAL=true
activate MCP

MCP -> MCP : NewMCPServer(nil)\n注册工具/资源/提示词
note right of MCP
  服务器以 nil DB 立即启动。
  MCP 握手不被任何数据库 I/O 阻塞。
  DB 就绪后通过 SetDB 热注入。
end note

MCP -> Job : goroutine: 后台初始化
activate Job

Job -> DB : InitDatabase(ctx, dbCfg)
activate DB
DB --> Job : *gorm.DB
deactivate DB

Job -> MCP : SetDB(db)\n热注入数据库连接

Job -> DB : MigrateAll(ctx)\n自动迁移三张表
DB --> Job : 迁移成功

Job -> Job : RunNow(ctx)\n立即执行首次同步

Job -> Circl : Run(ctx)
activate Circl
Circl -> CirclAPI : GET /vulnerability/?page=1&per_page=100
CirclAPI --> Circl : JSON { data: [...], total: N }
loop 分页抓取直到全部完成
    Circl -> CirclAPI : GET /vulnerability/?page=N
    CirclAPI --> Circl : JSON 第 N 页
end
Circl -> DB : BulkUpsert(ctx, []CirclCVE)\nCreateInBatches(100)\nOnConflict{UpdateAll:true}
DB --> Circl : 影响行数
deactivate Circl

Job -> Mycert : Run(ctx)
activate Mycert
Mycert -> MycertPortal : GET /advisories/list
MycertPortal --> Mycert : HTML 列表页
Mycert -> Mycert : 解析 HTML\n提取公告链接
loop 抓取详情页
    Mycert -> MycertPortal : GET /advisories/detail?id=X
    MycertPortal --> Mycert : HTML 详情页
end
Mycert -> DB : BulkUpsert(ctx, []MycertAdvisory)
DB --> Mycert : 影响行数
deactivate Mycert

Job -> Job : Start(ctx)\n注册 cron 表达式\n"0 */3 * * *"（每 3 小时）
deactivate Job

MCP -> MCP : Run(ctx)\nstdio 传输\n阻塞等待

' ============================================================
' 阶段二：AI 客户端工具调用 - get_cve
' ============================================================
== 阶段二：AI 客户端工具调用 - get_cve ==

Client -> MCP : MCP JSON-RPC 2.0\n{"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"get_cve","arguments":{"id":"CVE-2021-44228"}}}
activate MCP

MCP -> Actions : toolGetCVE(ctx, params{ID:"CVE-2021-44228"})
activate Actions

Actions -> DB : SELECT * FROM circl_cves\nWHERE cve_id = 'CVE-2021-44228'\nWITH CONTEXT(ctx)
activate DB
DB --> Actions : CirclCVE{...}
deactivate DB

Actions --> MCP : *mcp.CallToolResult\n{cve_id, title, severity, description, ...}
deactivate Actions

MCP --> Client : JSON-RPC 响应\n{result: {content: [{type:"text", text: "..."}]}}
deactivate MCP

' ============================================================
' 阶段三：AI 客户端工具调用 - search_cves
' ============================================================
== 阶段三：AI 客户端工具调用 - search_cves ==

Client -> MCP : tools/call search_cves\n{keyword:"log4j", severity:"critical", limit:20}
activate MCP

MCP -> Actions : toolSearchCVEs(ctx, SearchCVEsParams{...})
activate Actions

Actions -> DB : SELECT * FROM circl_cves\nWHERE (title LIKE '%log4j%'\n  OR description LIKE '%log4j%')\n  AND severity = 'critical'\nORDER BY date_published DESC\nLIMIT 20
DB --> Actions : []CirclCVE (N 条记录)

Actions --> MCP : {total: N, count: N, results: [...]}
deactivate Actions

MCP --> Client : JSON-RPC 响应
deactivate MCP

' ============================================================
' 阶段四：定时 Cron 同步（每 3 小时）
' ============================================================
== 阶段四：定时 Cron 同步（每 3 小时） ==

Job -> Circl : cron 触发: syncAll(ctx)
activate Circl
Circl -> CirclAPI : 分页抓取
CirclAPI --> Circl : 更新后的 CVE 数据
Circl -> DB : BulkUpsert（幂等操作）
deactivate Circl

Job -> Mycert : cron 触发
activate Mycert
Mycert -> MycertPortal : 爬取公告
MycertPortal --> Mycert : HTML
Mycert -> DB : BulkUpsert
deactivate Mycert

note over Job, DB
  所有 Upsert 使用 OnConflict{UpdateAll:true}。
  重复的 CVE ID 会原地更新，不会插入重复行。
  操作具有完全幂等性，可安全重复执行。
end note

@enduml
